                  <provenance>
                    Provenance, etc. This codex was donated to Trinity Western University in 1993 by Brian L. Fargher, who purchased it in Ethiopia in the 1960’s.
                    A placard that is inside the front cover states: “THE PSALMS OF DAVID Hand Written in Ancient Geez Language on Sheepskin Parchment—From Lake Tsana Island Monastery—Ethiopia.
                    Date Unknown—Probably pre 1700.”
                  </provenance>
